data.description: Welcome to this splendid 5-acre piece of property that combines the best of country living with modern comfort. Nestled in a serene, natural setting, this property features a spacious and well-maintained manufactured home that is designed with a split bedroom concept, offering the perfect balance of privacy and togetherness. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the generously proportioned living space, creating an inviting and open atmosphere for family gatherings and entertaining. The heart of this home is the large master suite, complete with ample closet space and a private en-suite bathroom. The property offers endless opportunities for outdoor activities. Don't miss your chance to make this your new home. Schedule your showing today!
